
                                         R U M M I K U B

                   RULES:
                    - you get 14 cards(tiles)
                    - you can make them in 123 order with the same color or 888 in different kolors
                    - each number represents number of points each card has
                    - the goal is to use up all of your cards by putting them on the table in the right sequences or adding card to the sequences that are already on the table
                    - you can start putting or adding any cards on the table when the points from the sequences you made are at least 30
                    - if you cant put anything on the table when your turn comes, you have to take one additional card
                    - at your turn, you can manipulate all sequences to your liking, granted, all cards you are using for manipulation are back on the table at the end of your turn